//! \page running Running TIO tool
//!
//! This page contains details of how to run TIO tool
//!
//! \section usage Usage
//!
//! \code{.sh}
//! tiotool [-h|--help] [-v|--version] [filename(s)]
//! \endcode
//!
//! \section options Options
//!
//! Here are the available options:
//!
//!
//! | Option              | Description                |
//! | :------------------ | :------------------------- |
//! | `filename(s)`       | list of input files        |
//! | `-h` \| `--help`    | prints usage information   |
//! | `-v` \| `--version` | prints version information |
//!
